name: Pokego.dev
tagline: Pokemon GO get player inventory and pokemon ivs/information by PHP - Laravel
body:
## About

Pokemon GO check user info and Pokemon IVs use PHP

- New pokedex Database
- Check pokemon 's move
- more...

## Requirements

- PHP >5.6
- Composer
- Git

## Install

```
(cd /server_http_path/)
git clone https://github.com/HadesD/PokeGO.DEV.git
cd /PokeGO.DEV/
composer install
cp .env.example .env
php artisan key:generate
```
Open browser to view
http://localhost/PokeGO.DEV/
